Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.81,0:00:06.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天亮了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.23,0:00:09.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明天亮了却还是很困
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.06,0:00:12.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.08,0:00:14.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明天亮了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.63,0:00:16.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的天亮了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.80,0:00:20.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许天还没亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.19,0:00:26.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛确实是天亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.74,0:00:28.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.30,0:00:00.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.12,0:02:05.65,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,590)\fad(500,500)}初雪火锅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.82,0:02:11.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  小唯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.47,0:02:13.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.47,0:02:15.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯你走路好快呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.41,0:02:19.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为好冷所以想早点到学校
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.08,0:02:22.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是特别的冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.74,0:02:23.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.70,0:02:25.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.33,0:02:31.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饶命饶命饶命！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.71,0:02:39.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.11,0:02:41.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.07,0:02:43.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.06,0:02:47.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.32,0:02:49.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.74,0:02:54.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好  这里是搞笑剧场
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.98,0:02:57.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晒到日光可以精神变好的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.49,0:02:59.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.49,0:03:07.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,窗户的影子部分不太暖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.19,0:03:08.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.07,0:03:16.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向阳的地方就是舒服呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.92,0:03:17.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.15,0:03:22.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太舒服了都变得慵懒不想动了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.01,0:03:24.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.92,0:03:27.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.22,0:03:31.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「土豆」这个词真好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.81,0:03:37.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「土豆」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.51,0:03:39.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「土豆」啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.65,0:03:42.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是「土豆」嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.15,0:03:53.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥  用煮烂的土豆啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.32,0:03:55.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要去掉皮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.10,0:03:58.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给穿得单薄的小唯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.53,0:04:01.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扔过去的话你会生气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.89,0:04:05.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那应该会吧…毕竟很烫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.49,0:04:07.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.78,0:04:09.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想扔扔看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.86,0:04:12.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是吃的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.67,0:04:13.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.40,0:04:19.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扔给你包含有「悄悄给你了」「请你吃」的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.22,0:04:21.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的说…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.22,0:04:26.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那反正要给的话就好好拿个好吃的给我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.61,0:04:30.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  某种意义上烫呼呼的很好吃啊  
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.69,0:04:33.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.13,0:04:37.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌讨厌  不要来这种反应啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.41,0:04:48.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴走族取名叫「土豆」怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.88,0:04:54.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱呀  日本第一可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.35,0:04:58.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真的很厉害哦  全关东第一哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.58,0:05:04.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为这暖和天气的原因吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.54,0:05:12.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  栎井同学怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.69,0:05:17.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小相  她没事的  完全没问题哟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.27,0:05:21.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体有没哪里出了问题？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.50,0:05:23.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.40,0:05:26.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土…豆…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.68,0:05:31.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.43,0:05:38.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂相川  刚才的笑声是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.51,0:05:43.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是栎井她们？那声音有够大的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.10,0:05:48.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说  好像是因为「土豆」的梗而笑趴了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.07,0:05:51.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？那是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.86,0:05:55.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那三个家伙果然很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.20,0:05:58.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.08,0:06:06.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.59,0:06:07.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.81,0:06:13.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷冷冷冷…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.13,0:06:14.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开暖气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.70,0:06:22.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这叫…暖气
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.91,0:06:25.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你朋友吗？  这么得瑟！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.82,0:06:30.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暖炉它…是个好家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.01,0:06:31.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家伙？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.16,0:06:37.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是因为太费电了  所以也算是个败家的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.67,0:06:46.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是星期几呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.82,0:06:49.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.40,0:06:51.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期四
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.36,0:06:54.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.84,0:06:58.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？为啥突然冒出个「原来如此」来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.98,0:07:02.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥…星期四是不是有这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.94,0:07:06.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是「土豆」的感觉  热气腾腾的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.75,0:07:09.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是土豆也有周六的要素
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.27,0:07:12.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.12,0:07:14.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「真的啊」是什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.00,0:07:17.25,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}今日主题  星期
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.81,0:07:22.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期六  Saturday是从农业之神——萨杜恩一词而来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.81,0:07:22.24,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(860,630)}Saruen
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.40,0:07:24.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就说嘛  所以土豆是星期六
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.01,0:07:25.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.36,0:07:30.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是土豆真的很热气腾腾的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.12,0:07:34.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才就一直在说的「mokumoku」是啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.12,0:07:34.54,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}「mokumoku」形容热气腾腾状
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.82,0:07:38.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那第2第4就是星期四啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.81,0:07:40.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.59,0:07:42.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.31,0:07:46.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那星期四是什么样的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.79,0:07:54.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期四  Thursday来自北欧神话里的雷神托尔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.96,0:07:55.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.00,0:07:59.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家用游戏机发售日
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.35,0:08:02.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多周刊漫画的发行日
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.98,0:08:05.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个好日子呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.70,0:08:06.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.92,0:08:11.05,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}具注历是平安时代流行于奈良的一种历书，起源于我国。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.92,0:08:11.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在具注历中似乎把星期天写成「密」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.57,0:08:12.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,密
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.86,0:08:15.45,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}「ミール」在古粟特语中是星期天的意思。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.86,0:08:15.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是把「ミール」转写成的汉字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.14,0:08:16.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,密
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.66,0:08:20.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉有点邪恶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.00,0:08:22.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.69,0:08:24.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.17,0:08:29.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  下一个密要怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.06,0:08:33.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:36.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯  下一个密现在有空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.40,0:08:40.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,密要做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.25,0:08:45.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,密做点什么吧密啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.88,0:08:47.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  密啊密的吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.71,0:08:56.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用蔡勒公式的话  就可以从日期直接计算出星期几来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.11,0:09:00.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那1999年呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.61,0:09:05.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  用蔡勒式计算就明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.88,0:09:11.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那2020年的1月1日呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.79,0:09:14.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个也用蔡勒公式计算就明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.05,0:09:14.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我好好回答
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.83,0:09:21.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期天作为休息日  而且人们以星期为标准而生活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.32,0:09:24.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在明治时代引入西历后出现的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.34,0:09:30.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那那个呢  美容院什么的要怎样才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.16,0:09:32.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠猜？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.17,0:09:35.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天好像是星期二所以休息？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.36,0:09:38.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说以前的人有星期几的概念吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.46,0:09:42.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的人都是家里蹲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.85,0:09:49.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚子同学  拜托你做总结
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.23,0:09:50.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.52,0:09:56.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把边框的装饰留着可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.10,0:09:57.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.88,0:10:00.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那总结就是
