Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.77,0:10:03.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个感觉不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.79,0:10:07.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  柚子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.23,0:10:12.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说我越来越不懂「mokumoku」了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:13.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要第2就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.04,0:10:15.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.81,0:10:17.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始就不懂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.22,0:10:20.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走廊好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.65,0:10:23.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很冷就变得想吃火锅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.56,0:10:24.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔！想吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.18,0:10:27.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在社团活动室里搞火锅Party吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:29.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  很不错的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.92,0:10:30.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个提议好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.91,0:10:35.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用砂锅怎么样  把桌炉带来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.85,0:10:37.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好暖和呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.71,0:10:40.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是老师绝对不肯的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.24,0:10:43.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不知道呢  去说说看？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.58,0:10:46.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便携式瓦斯炉什么的应该有吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.43,0:10:47.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦斯炉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.45,0:10:51.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈借个火给我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.33,0:10:52.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.36,0:10:53.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锁骨…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.04,0:10:57.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  具体说就是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.32,0:11:01.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦斯炉啊  吓死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.29,0:11:05.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的请不要吓老师好吗  因为真的会吓到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.12,0:11:08.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.04,0:11:12.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓到了  老师被你们吓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.81,0:11:14.22,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来她很怕被吓到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.97,0:11:18.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈  可以在社团活动室里煮火锅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.40,0:11:20.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.22,0:11:22.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.08,0:11:25.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这么说但是实际上是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.31,0:11:26.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.17,0:11:33.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈  你肩膀上有一只红蜘蛛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.77,0:11:38.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一副骗人的表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.84,0:11:40.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.42,0:11:41.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.06,0:11:47.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮帮帮…我拿掉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.32,0:11:49.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得不能动弹了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.65,0:11:52.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮你拿下来的话就能够吃火锅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.08,0:11:54.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.25,0:11:57.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然什么都不说的我也很那啥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.87,0:11:59.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.36,0:12:02.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好伟大的老师啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.40,0:12:05.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我骗您的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.91,0:12:09.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？那就是说没有红蜘蛛喽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.49,0:12:14.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.07,0:12:16.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.96,0:12:19.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么下次去妈妈家吃火锅呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.75,0:12:22.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话没问题哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.31,0:12:27.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  前一天要和我约好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.75,0:12:29.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得先收拾一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.78,0:12:32.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.69,0:12:36.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  一切都解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.48,0:12:37.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.68,0:12:41.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠悠式
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.10,0:12:44.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么大家请吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.93,0:12:46.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们开动喽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.31,0:12:49.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  这个真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.50,0:12:51.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圆圆的！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.66,0:12:53.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很烫的你们小心一点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.76,0:12:56.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔  这个就是传说中的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.50,0:12:58.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个也能吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.72,0:12:59.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.04,0:13:01.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个也放进去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.50,0:13:02.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.48,0:13:04.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔  这个就是传说中的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.32,0:13:05.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好吵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.15,0:13:06.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圆圆的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.64,0:13:07.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说中的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:10.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  那么合上双掌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.12,0:13:13.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.63,0:13:16.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  太好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.43,0:13:17.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.62,0:13:19.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.33,0:13:22.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后的面也很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.50,0:13:24.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.75,0:13:26.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别把被子弄脏了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.54,0:13:28.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟汉堡肉一样好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.75,0:13:31.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不懂你的标准啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.51,0:13:33.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我老妈做的水平一样哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.36,0:13:35.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你家人才能懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.36,0:13:37.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面有煎蛋哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.29,0:13:39.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是放煎蛋的问题啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.40,0:13:40.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和风萝卜泥哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.89,0:13:43.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  这个  虽然我很喜欢…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.37,0:13:45.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买单的时候能送你口香糖哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.51,0:13:46.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个店情况不同啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.03,0:13:49.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家的路上去一趟便利店怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.02,0:13:52.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃得这么饱  稍微逛一下就好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.33,0:13:54.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么顺便去一趟加油站怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.85,0:13:56.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  总觉得很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.83,0:13:58.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那明天准备做什…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.07,0:13:58.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火锅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.51,0:14:03.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  弄得这么吵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.23,0:14:07.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  偶尔一次而已…大概
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.46,0:14:14.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈在学校的形象和平时的形象果然有些不同吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.63,0:14:16.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.96,0:14:19.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可爱？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.06,0:14:22.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.98,0:14:26.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橱柜可以打开看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.76,0:14:28.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.12,0:14:42.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  她好像很想看的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.52,0:14:51.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒假我会好好做作业的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.36,0:14:53.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会好好做哦  足足做四页哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.08,0:14:54.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好少
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.07,0:14:57.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我出五页的话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.73,0:15:00.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.05,0:15:03.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下是野野原
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.82,0:15:05.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.01,0:15:08.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.87,0:15:09.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.19,0:15:12.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.78,0:15:14.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.81,0:15:15.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.81,0:15:19.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就要到圣诞节了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.40,0:15:22.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.66,0:15:24.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年也去小唯家住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.49,0:15:29.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  为什么还要特地说一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.56,0:15:33.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  你们到什么时候还相信有圣诞老人？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.72,0:15:35.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惯例问题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.54,0:15:36.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好土
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.16,0:15:40.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话题  怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.89,0:15:44.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.19,0:15:55.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞节去小唯家  要带些什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.08,0:15:56.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.08,0:15:59.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要用这么笨蛋的语气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.44,0:16:02.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  大家穿上发光睡衣睡觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.58,0:16:03.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.74,0:16:04.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都几岁了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.89,0:16:06.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来也也没有我们能穿的尺码吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.73,0:16:11.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.96,0:16:14.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  想发光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.39,0:16:17.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想发光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.85,0:16:21.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发光  发光！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.68,0:16:24.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好恶心呃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.49,0:16:28.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  发光内衣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.53,0:16:30.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了什么存在的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.53,0:16:33.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  发光的墙纸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.93,0:16:34.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着好阴暗！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.39,0:16:37.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么闪耀的未来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.90,0:16:39.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己去争取吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.73,0:16:41.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢！好棒的回复
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.42,0:16:42.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发光的回复
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.71,0:16:47.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说小唯才是最闪耀的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.34,0:16:49.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.71,0:16:51.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得害羞起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.99,0:16:52.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栎井
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.67,0:16:57.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很厉害嘛  说得这么快…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.72,0:16:58.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.11,0:17:00.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈酱…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.16,0:17:03.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈…冈野同学  你听到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.51,0:17:04.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.22,0:17:11.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别老是拐走我家的相川
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.06,0:17:16.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞节准备怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.10,0:17:18.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  在我家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.90,0:17:20.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在小唯家过夜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.39,0:17:25.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.37,0:17:28.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要和相川她们出去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.70,0:17:30.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.08,0:17:34.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.12,0:17:35.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.61,0:17:37.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.90,0:17:43.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  第一场雪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.76,0:17:46.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到雪那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.96,0:17:47.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪球
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.85,0:17:48.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气球
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.85,0:17:50.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想干什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.51,0:17:51.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.10,0:18:02.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小的时候我一直在想气球上面到底积多少雪才会飘不起来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.82,0:18:08.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在我做别的事情的时候就不知道飘哪儿去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.23,0:18:12.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.69,0:18:17.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果就这样没了三四个气球
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.35,0:18:18.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.95,0:18:21.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子的脑袋就跟气球一样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.95,0:18:24.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像气球一样的脑袋的女孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.43,0:18:25.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空荡荡的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.12,0:18:30.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我突然想起了很小的时候的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.11,0:18:33.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我也不知道的时候吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.89,0:18:36.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好像是小学一年级左右吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.20,0:18:39.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在想起来还觉得真是没有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.70,0:18:45.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时觉得从天上落下来的雪花掺杂着死去动物的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.86,0:18:48.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得如果在雪里待太久人就会变得奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.44,0:18:51.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  是不是有点不对劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.51,0:18:56.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是吧  就是那种怪孩子啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.47,0:18:57.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.22,0:19:04.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯你看  那片奇怪的雪花掺杂着沙钻鱼的灵魂哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.73,0:19:05.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.60,0:19:06.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鱼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.20,0:19:17.56,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}沙钻鱼「鱚」音同kiss
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.20,0:19:17.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那个kiss不同啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.81,0:19:19.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白痴吗  你是白痴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.94,0:19:21.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缘  快来帮帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.88,0:19:26.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚子  现在有未知的灵魂侵占了柚子的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.41,0:19:33.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好有礼貌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.62,0:19:34.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未知的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.74,0:19:39.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这雪会不会积下来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.90,0:19:41.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还下得很小呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.93,0:19:45.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实刚才进入我身体的是神哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.49,0:19:46.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.51,0:19:49.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我祈祷的话雪会马上变大
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.26,0:19:52.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么请神给我钱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.76,0:19:54.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这什么人！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.53,0:19:56.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？雪是不是停了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.97,0:19:57.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.76,0:20:00.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  就这样停了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.82,0:20:02.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.50,0:20:04.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神  快下雪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.19,0:20:06.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好麻烦的人类啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.64,0:20:09.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么钱就不需要了呗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.93,0:20:10.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个都要！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.29,0:20:14.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢  你也太人类了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.35,0:20:16.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？不行吗  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.93,0:20:18.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好诚实的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.44,0:20:22.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又开始下了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.73,0:20:25.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊  神好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.74,0:20:27.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.79,0:20:31.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.29,0:20:36.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啊  神什么的是骗你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.78,0:20:38.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  真是麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.33,0:20:49.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是神
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.84,0:20:53.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘着这片雪降临于人世
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.96,0:20:55.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果触碰到有生命的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.39,0:20:59.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就会带来奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.96,0:21:13.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缘  走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.50,0:21:14.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  这就走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.85,0:21:18.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说笑的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.37,0:21:26.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.22,0:21:30.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个那个  说点夏天的话题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.14,0:21:32.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊  不错的话题呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.86,0:21:38.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了  想不出好的了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.05,0:21:40.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nice fight
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.25,0:21:41.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为太冷了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.21,0:21:44.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.93,0:21:46.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.45,0:21:49.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.24,0:21:53.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  冬天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.76,0:21:56.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬天太冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.91,0:23:33.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栎树的果实又红又甜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.44,0:23:34.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,种子里还有毒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.66,0:23:35.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.33,0:23:37.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我还是要吃  小唯的果实
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.54,0:23:38.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红红的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.44,0:23:39.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  不要吃啊
